---
---

<section
  id="top"
  class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-20 md:pb-28 border-b border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7">
      <div data-fi class="opacity-0 flex items-center gap-3 mb-10">
        <span
          class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span
            class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-600 rounded-full animate-pulse-dot"
          ></span>
          Disponible · Abril 2026
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1
        data-fi
        style="animation-delay:.05s"
        class="opacity-0 tracking-[-0.03em] text-[clamp(2.75rem,6vw,5.25rem)] font-light leading-[0.98] mb-10"
      >
        Software Engineering Lead<br />
        <span class="text-fp-dim">con diez años diseñando sistemas</span><br />
        que no se caen.
      </h1>
      <p
        data-fi
        style="animation-delay:.1s"
        class="opacity-0 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-fp-ink2 dark:text-fp-dfg/85"
      >
        Mi experiencia está enfocada en diseñar y evolucionar
        arquitecturas de microservicios con .NET y Java Spring Boot,
        construyendo interfaces en Angular y React, y llevando
        soluciones a entornos cloud como AWS y Azure. Me muevo con
        naturalidad entre la arquitectura, la ejecución técnica y el
        liderazgo de equipos, con foco en escalabilidad, estabilidad y
        productos que responden bien bajo presión.
      </p>

      <div
        data-fi
        style="animation-delay:.15s"
        class="opacity-0 mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3"
      >
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-fp-ink text-fp-bg dark:bg-fp-dfg dark:text-fp-dbg text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
        >
          Conversemos
          <svg
            class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2.5"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#experience"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 border border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline hover:border-fp-ink dark:hover:border-fp-dfg transition-colors text-sm font-medium"
        >
          Ver experiencia
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/10lGNZ5J3l_LcxfvfNNqwBOFz8_EA8NT_/view?usp=drive_link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-fp-dim hover:text-fp-ink dark:hover:text-fp-dfg transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          CV.pdf
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 h-px bg-fp-line dark:bg-fp-dline"></div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div data-fi style="animation-delay:.2s" class="opacity-0">
          <div
            class="tracking-[-0.03em] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono tabular-nums font-light"
          >
            <span data-counter="10">0</span>+
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mt-2"
          >
            Años
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-fi style="animation-delay:.22s" class="opacity-0">
          <div
            class="tracking-[-0.03em] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono tabular-nums font-light"
          >
            <span data-counter="1">0</span>M+
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mt-2"
          >
            Req/día
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-fi style="animation-delay:.24s" class="opacity-0">
          <div
            class="tracking-[-0.03em] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono tabular-nums font-light"
          >
            99.9%
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mt-2"
          >
            Uptime
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-fi style="animation-delay:.26s" class="opacity-0">
          <div
            class="tracking-[-0.03em] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono tabular-nums font-light"
          >
            <span data-counter="-80">0</span>%
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mt-2"
          >
            Bugs
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside
      class="opacity-0 col-span-12 md:col-span-5 md:pl-6 lg:pl-10"
      data-fi
      style="animation-delay:.1s"
    >
      <figure class="relative group">
        <div
          class="relative overflow-hidden bg-fp-panel dark:bg-fp-dpanel border border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline aspect-[3/4]"
        >
          <img
            src="/portrait.webp"
            alt="Carlos Mayorga Hilario — retrato"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-all duration-[1.2s] group-hover:scale-[1.02] dark:brightness-90 dark:contrast-110"
          />
          <span
            class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-3 h-3 border-t border-l border-fp-ink/40 dark:border-fp-dfg/40"
          ></span>
          <span
            class="absolute top-3 right-3 w-3 h-3 border-t border-r border-fp-ink/40 dark:border-fp-dfg/40"
          ></span>
          <span
            class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 w-3 h-3 border-b border-l border-fp-ink/40 dark:border-fp-dfg/40"
          ></span>
          <span
            class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 w-3 h-3 border-b border-r border-fp-ink/40 dark:border-fp-dfg/40"
          ></span>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-4 py-3 bg-fp-bg/90 dark:bg-fp-dbg/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline flex items-center justify-between"
          >
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium"
              >Portrait · 2026</span
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-fp-dim">LIMA · 12°S</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <div
              class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mb-1"
            >
              Retrato
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm leading-snug">
              Carlos Mayorga Hilario<br />
              <span class="text-fp-dim">Software Engineering Lead</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-mono text-[10px] text-fp-dim whitespace-nowrap text-right"
          >
            <div>REF. 001</div>
            <div class="mt-1">03 / 2026</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <div
    class="mt-14 md:mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-0 border border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
  >
    <div
      class="opacity-0 px-8 py-7 border-b border-r border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
      data-fi
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mb-2"
      >
        Ubicación
      </div>
      <div class="text-base">
        Lima, Perú<br /><span class="text-fp-dim text-sm">Remoto disponible</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="opacity-0 px-8 py-7 border-b md:border-r border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
      data-fi
      style="animation-delay:.05s"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mb-2"
      >
        Experiencia
      </div>
      <div class="text-base">
        10+ años<br /><span class="text-fp-dim text-sm">Backend · Arquitectura</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="opacity-0 px-8 py-7 border-b border-r border-t md:border-t-0 border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
      data-fi
      style="animation-delay:.1s"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mb-2"
      >
        Idiomas
      </div>
      <div class="text-base">
        Español <span class="text-fp-dim">nativo</span><br />Inglés
        <span class="text-fp-dim">B1</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="opacity-0 px-8 py-7 border-b border-t md:border-t-0 border-fp-line dark:border-fp-dline"
      data-fi
      style="animation-delay:.15s"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-fp-dim font-medium mb-2"
      >
        Enfoque actual
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm leading-snug">
        Tech Lead · Staff Engineer · Solutions Architect
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
